---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Valyrian Tech BV - how we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-valyrian-100 mb-8 text-center">
        Privacy <span class="text-gradient">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      
      <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="prose-valyrian">
          <p>
            This Privacy Policy explains how Valyrian Tech BV collects, uses, and discloses your information when you access or use our services and website.
          </p>

          <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Company name:</strong> Valyrian Tech BV</li>
            <li><strong>Contact email address:</strong> info@valyrian.tech</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect data necessary to provide and improve our services. This may include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Other information you provide us</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We also use technologies like cookies and web server logs to collect usage information such as:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>The date and time of your visit</li>
            <li>The pages you view</li>
            <li>Your IP address</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <p>We use your data to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
            <li>Respond to your inquiries</li>
            <li>Send you updates and information about our services</li>
            <li>Security, administrative, and legal purposes</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Cookies are small text files stored on your device to help us improve your experience on our website. You can manage your cookie settings in your browser, but note that some parts of our services may not function properly without them.
          </p>

          <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Correct your personal data</li>
            <li>Delete your personal data</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict our processing of your data</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@valyrian.tech">info@valyrian.tech</a>.</p>

          <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes and will always have the most current policy posted on our website.
          </p>

          <hr class="border-valyrian-600/30 my-8" />

          <p class="text-sm text-valyrian-400">
            Please note that by using our services, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your information as described in this Privacy Policy. If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us at <strong>info@valyrian.tech</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
